<div id="review_33813658" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/33813658" />
    <a title="Christopher" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/265016-christopher"><img alt="Christopher" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1243535349p2/265016.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/33813658?book_show_action=true">Sep 25, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Christopher" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Christopher" href="/user/show/265016-christopher">Christopher</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer33813658" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10015296659188766308">This was an ok read. It gives good insight into life in Poland during socialism, the fear, the distrust, the apathy. As a novel however, I find that it drifts a little listlessly to and fro, and I found myself caring little for any of the characters.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

